{"title":"OneUp Flexes Oval Aluminum Handlebar for More Affordable Vertical Compliance","link":"https://bikerumor.com/oneup-oval-aluminum-handlebar-direct-mount-stem/","date":1687968000000,"content":"<p>OneUp Components has recreated the patented oval shape of its premium carbon handlebar in an aluminum offering, bringing the price of this additional cockpit compliance down to a more-easy-to-swallow $89.50 USD. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>OneUp Aluminum Handlebar</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Unique to OneUp’s handlebars is the ovalized section that exists between the 35mm clamp region and the 22.2mm control-clamping region. The profile allows for additional flex in this area, versus a standard bar that is traditionally circular in this zone. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-oval-handlebar-direct-mount-stem.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-oval-handlebar-direct-mount-stem-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"oneup-oval-alloy handlebar vertical compliance comfort reduced fatigue\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-oval-handlebar-direct-mount-stem-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-oval-handlebar-direct-mount-stem-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-oval-handlebar-direct-mount-stem-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-oval-handlebar-direct-mount-stem-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-oval-handlebar-direct-mount-stem-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-oval-handlebar-direct-mount-stem-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-oval-handlebar-direct-mount-stem.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>I’ve been lucky enough to benefit from the OneUp Carbon Bar for some time, now. I’m kind of spoiled with it, in a way, because whenever I have to switch to a test bike with a standard aluminum or carbon bar, I often feel the unwelcome return of arm pump over longer descents. I really appreciate the extra comfort that comes with a bit of vertical compliance.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Until now, you would’ve been required to part with $159.50 USD in order to benefit from the ovalised bar profile, but the addition of the One Oval Aluminum Handlebar brings the price down to something far more palatable. Deflection of the alloy bar at a given weight is just 6% less than that for the carbon offering.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The OneUp Alloy Bar ships at 800mm wide, and weighs 341 grams on our Park Tool scale. That weight pertains to the 35mm rise option, which for now is the only option. However, August 2023 will see the inclusion of a 20mm riser bar of the same oval design. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-cut-marks-750mm-minimum.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-cut-marks-750mm-minimum-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"oneup alloy bar cut marks 740mm minimum\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-cut-marks-750mm-minimum-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-cut-marks-750mm-minimum-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-cut-marks-750mm-minimum-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-cut-marks-750mm-minimum-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-cut-marks-750mm-minimum-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-cut-marks-750mm-minimum-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-cut-marks-750mm-minimum.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The 7050-T76 aluminum bar is intended for gravity riding, first and foremost. It is rated for downhill riding, with ASTM Cat. 5 and EFBE TRI-TEST® GR certifications.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Markings are provided on the bar ends to help riders in cutting the bar down to their preferred width; 740mm is the minimum width approved by OneUp. The maximum clamp width is 80mm.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-aluminum-oval-handlebar-vertical-compliance.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-aluminum-oval-handlebar-vertical-compliance-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"oneup direct mount stem 45mm length with aluminum oval handlebar dh approved\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-aluminum-oval-handlebar-vertical-compliance-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-aluminum-oval-handlebar-vertical-compliance-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-aluminum-oval-handlebar-vertical-compliance-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-aluminum-oval-handlebar-vertical-compliance-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-aluminum-oval-handlebar-vertical-compliance-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-aluminum-oval-handlebar-vertical-compliance-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-aluminum-oval-handlebar-vertical-compliance.jpg 1600w\" /></a><figcaption>The OneUp Aluminum Oval Handlebar retails at $89.50 USD / $119.50 CAD / £79.50 GBP / €89.50 EU</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>OneUp Direct Mount Stem</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In conjunction with the launch of the OneUp Oval Alloy Bar is the addition of a Direct Mount Stem to the BC-based brand’s portfolio. This one has a clamp diameter of 35mm, a length of 45mm and a 0mm rise, though 5mm and 10mm rise will be possible come August when specific spacer kits become available.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-dm-stem-150623-00879.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-dm-stem-150623-00879-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"oneup direct mount stem for dh forks 35mm clamp 45mm reach\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-dm-stem-150623-00879-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-dm-stem-150623-00879-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-dm-stem-150623-00879-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-dm-stem-150623-00879-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-dm-stem-150623-00879-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-dm-stem-150623-00879-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-alloy-bar-dm-stem-150623-00879.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Additional specs as follows:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Claimed weight: 155g</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Material: 6061-T6 Aluminum</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Finish: Fine shot peen</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Color Options: Black</li>\n\n\n\n<li>MSRP: $99.50 USD / $129.50 CAD / £99.50 GBP / €114.50 EU</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>OneUp offer free shipping worldwide.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-direct-mount-stem-0mm-5mm-10mm-rise-with-spacer-kit.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-direct-mount-stem-0mm-5mm-10mm-rise-with-spacer-kit-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"oneup-direct-mount stem 0mm rise with spacer kit 5mm 10mm options\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-direct-mount-stem-0mm-5mm-10mm-rise-with-spacer-kit-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-direct-mount-stem-0mm-5mm-10mm-rise-with-spacer-kit-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-direct-mount-stem-0mm-5mm-10mm-rise-with-spacer-kit-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-direct-mount-stem-0mm-5mm-10mm-rise-with-spacer-kit-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-direct-mount-stem-0mm-5mm-10mm-rise-with-spacer-kit-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-direct-mount-stem-0mm-5mm-10mm-rise-with-spacer-kit-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/oneup-direct-mount-stem-0mm-5mm-10mm-rise-with-spacer-kit.jpg 1600w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.oneupcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">oneupcomponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/oneup-oval-aluminum-handlebar-direct-mount-stem/\">OneUp Flexes Oval Aluminum Handlebar for More Affordable Vertical Compliance</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"3b05437e4296acf4808519f33a3c142df413943ec3c0110defbb9c2347493ec9","category":"Cycling"}